{"tid":788821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦用緊TP Link Archer T4U今日突然上唔到網咁濟","createTime":"2018-08-21T18:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T10:06:15.000Z","uid":170879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e04ffb4e1c94cbc1f1a981b321568fa36fd41a6b","tid":788821,"uid":170879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T18:57:46.000Z","msg":"部機用咗一段時間 一直用TP Link隻USB手指連WIFI無問題 都半年左右<br />\n點知今晚一返嚟開機用就出事<br />\n部機係連到Wifi同埋Signal係爆<br />\n問題嚟喇 上網一樣係喺極慢同上唔到之間遊走<br />\n試過重灌windows同埋隻usb driver都唔得<br />\n上網試download同upload speed都測唔到<br />\n<br />\n神奇嘅地方係我有一兩次抆完隻usb重插嗰陣變返正常上網速 但係維持唔夠半分鐘又瞓返底<br />\n<br />\n全屋手機 其他電腦都無事<br />\n有無巴打知咩事可以救救小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:大半個電腦白痴"},{"pid":"f124826fa6093c53a5136d3035e93a0de921e90b","tid":788821,"uid":57214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T18:58:35.000Z","msg":"TP Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc465106ab5e1b8d277b776d10a924f2bf8a3f2","tid":788821,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T18:59:17.000Z","msg":"用大陸LINK當然啦"},{"pid":"a97a661e682052a3094ef67c6f0ea5a358a68d16","tid":788821,"uid":170879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f124826fa6093c53a5136d3035e93a0de921e90b","tid":788821,"uid":57214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T18:58:35.000Z","msg":"TP Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T19:01:36.000Z","msg":"當日畀朋友水咗去買 咁嘅情況係咪可以扔咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216561b112fe3b2a34b83f57b00ece516157c218","tid":788821,"uid":170879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc465106ab5e1b8d277b776d10a924f2bf8a3f2","tid":788821,"uid":99205,"l